https://gcc.gnu.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=65863
-> huh?
https://gcc.gnu.org/ml/gcc-help/2016-06/msg00016.html
- > yes, this is the inicatition I needed, mpfr, gmp and mpc point to a weird location

